incident_updates.body:
A fix has been implemented.
We don't see any impact related to this incident.
We are monitoring the issue.
Update : Our teams are still working on a fix to solve the problem.
Update : Our teams continue to work on the correction. Updates will be posted as soon as significant progress is made.

Start time : 27/09/2022 15:30 UTC Service impact : For some customers, ordering Additionnal IPs via the API or the manager may not be possible. Root cause : A migration has impacted the SoYouStart and Kimsufi APIs. Ongoing actions : A fix is currently in progress. Workaround : You may contact the support team directly if you are impacted by this incident. They will be able to create Additional IPs orders for you.

Start time : 13/03/2023 05:30 UTC End time : 13/03/2023 06:30 UTC Service impact : The public network will be unavailable during maintenance. Service improvement : Our teams will replace a switch on the S332B07 rack.

Start time : 13/03/2023 20:30 UTC End time : 13/03/2023 23:59 UTC Service impact : Servers will be temporarily unreachable for 30 minutes during the maintenance. Service improvement : As part of our continuous improvement policy of our network infrastructure, we are rolling out an upgrade to several devices of network equipment.
